{"tid":1986862,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"IT男涉拒捕 稱遭警打致留醫八日","createTime":"2020-04-24T06:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T06:23:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7b39abdd9d4c2c9c6c8527dd5fa9646e2d870547","tid":1986862,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:06:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200424/YE5V4FJ4GVKXL2AONIFKOBYFWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200424%2FYE5V4FJ4GVKXL2AONIFKOBYFWQ%2F&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hX%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=ff317924\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200424%2FYE5V4FJ4GVKXL2AONIFKOBYFWQ%2F&h=cb926805\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200424/YE5V4FJ4GVKXL2AONIFKOBYFWQ/</a><br />\n<br />\nIT男涉拒捕 稱遭警打致留醫八日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200424/large/1587659516_3b7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200424%2Flarge%2F1587659516_3b7e.jpg&h=0bed402e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁霆<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】市民去年10月發起「追究警暴」集會，其後演變成警民衝突，多人被捕。一名電腦程式設計師被捕時疑多番掙扎傷及警員，最終被控拒捕。辯方投訴指設計師被捕後，遭警員毆打致留醫八天，並不滿控方拒絕透露控罪中涉案警員的身份，裁判官劉淑嫻亦質疑有關做法。<br />\n<br />\n稱被五警毆 抹車工申認人<br />\n<br />\n被告梁霆（31歲）被指去年10月27日在旺角近奶路臣街交界抗拒警員A。控方解釋因案件涉及社會事件，故將警員匿名，裁判官將於6月17日處理有關匿名事宜。辯方昨亦指，警員要求梁先簽署口供紙才可見律師。<br />\n<br />\n此外，去年12月15日有示威者於旺角聚集堵路及縱火，其間抹車工人林澤光（33歲）被指用激光筆射向警車，並透過玻璃照射警員，被控襲警。<br />\n<br />\n辯方稱林在警車上遭五名警員毆打，會申請在審訊前進行非正式認人手續以辨識五警身份，並爭議警誡供詞自願性。案件提堂時辯方投訴稱林被捕後遭警員拳打、近距離用強光射眼五分鐘，以及延誤逾24小時才可見律師。林昨否認襲警及管有攻擊性武器兩罪。襲警罪原指林在雅蘭中心一期外襲擊警長3236，控方昨將警長3236改為「警員A」。林另被指管有一支雷射筆。辯方反對控方申請將涉案警員匿名，案件6月10日開審，屆時將一併處理匿名令。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC4604/19、878/20"},{"pid":"e3576cff13398fd43b33cc52b7942abbab6ffd28","tid":1986862,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />IT之光"},{"pid":"1303422e3d2c17b33a40662e819de612bbaee3f9","tid":1986862,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c94a071e7a307eb6bad47289d92869b69faa42","tid":1986862,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"警察如果私人檢控成功應該坐幾多年？"},{"pid":"3bbafe3a19f07fbe21cc6f5b4dc0bd6c6ec28b66","tid":1986862,"uid":233193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:11:03.000Z","msg":"拒捕咪又係老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班死黑警"},{"pid":"b6c4a79a16bcda722f7c13d7893acc3079b91c2e","tid":1986862,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49c94a071e7a307eb6bad47289d92869b69faa42","tid":1986862,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"警察如果私人檢控成功應該坐幾多年？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:11:45.000Z","msg":"唔洗坐<br />\n<br />\n終身剝奪私人財產權 + 不受法律保護人身安全就得"},{"pid":"4c03740381e277917ca48be15ac304a559d4a581","tid":1986862,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:14:06.000Z","msg":"勇武 IT！"},{"pid":"027a5836fde36a16572178ef8710dc64532b3f6e","tid":1986862,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:16:38.000Z","msg":"3236"},{"pid":"1fd3f5674f4b6baa2a1fa53da9b71dd3a5eb62e1","tid":1986862,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:23:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">狗長3236</span></strong>"}]}